If you do not save your account and only ever use Oky offline, you can still use the app. You can access your account and all your period information, as long as you don''t log out or log in on a different phone.', '1', 'en'), ('0bdcf661-31e7-4f37-b0dc-3be73b1a5613', '1c94b11a-53aa-49b7-8835-26dd780c7eff', 'e06a70fa-084a-4157-9ef6-f431205fdff2', 'Why is this app heavier than other apps on my phone?', 'While most apps only work online, Oky also works offline with no internet connection, so it needs all its content stored on the phone.
 
